{"id":58,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":58,"title":"Chapter 53: Moroni and His Teachings","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 53","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 53"],["h1","Moroni and His Teachings"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p3"},"After Mormon died, Moroni was alone. He finished the records his father had given him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.1,3"},"Mormon 8:1, 3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p5"},"Moroni knew the gold plates would one day be taken out of the ground."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.16"},"Mormon 8:16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p7"},"The words on the gold plates tell about Jesus Christ. They bear testimony and teach people how to live righteously."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/9.11-12,27"},"Mormon 9:11–12, 27"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p9"},"The wicked Lamanites killed every Nephite who would not deny Jesus Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.2"},"Moroni 1:2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p11"},"Moroni would never deny Jesus Christ. He moved around, hiding from the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.3"},"Moroni 1:3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p13"},"Moroni wrote more on the gold plates, especially to the Lamanites of the latter days."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.4"},"Moroni 1:4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p15"},"He wrote many important things, including the words of the sacrament prayers."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/4.title"},"Moroni 4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/5.title"},"Moroni 5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p17"},"Moroni wrote that the only people who can be baptized are those willing to repent of their sins and serve Jesus Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.1-3"},"Moroni 6:1–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p19"},"Moroni wanted everyone to believe in Jesus Christ and come to know him. He said everything good comes from Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.18,30"},"Moroni 10:18, 30"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p21"},"Moroni wrote that if people love God and follow him, they can become perfect."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32"},"Moroni 10:32"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_058_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p23"},"Moroni knew that after he died he would be resurrected and would live with Heavenly Father and Jesus Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-53-moroni-and-his-teachings.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.34"},"Moroni 10:34"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
